== Document generation ==

1. Take a document.
2. Extract the tags from the document. (remove the code for them?)
3. Generate tags using the tag generation table.
4. Generate HTML <meta> tags.
5. Convert the document format (using the format converter).
6. Calculate the name of the new file.
7. Inject the converted document into a copy of the template with name determined in [6].
8. Replace all tags.
9. Copy assets.
